ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectCreation of Ulkah Indian Reserve No. 3 (British Columbia)
PrecisOrder setting apart 59.62 hectares (147.32 acres) of land, for the use and benefit of the NAZKO FIRST NATION, formely known as the NAZKO INDIAN BAND, as ULKAH INDIAN RESERVE No. 3, in British Columbia.
